title: You Know, That Summer Job
description:
by snowtigra

A summer job, the bane of Katsuki’s existence, but he had to admit he’d brought it on himself. If he’d been smart he wouldn’t have snapped and yelled at his mother when she mentioned him spending another summer at their textile shop- he knew better dammit. She was never one to bluff with her threats. So Katsuki’s stuck painting and picking up supplies from the local hardware store where he finds some unexpected eye candy.

Previously posted on Twitter as a headcanon.

title: Así Se Verá The Big 3 En La Cuarta Temporada De Boku No Hero Academia #Anime #BokuNoHeroAcademia #shironodesaina #nekodemonio #CorporativoArcanos #Noticias
body:
Gracias a la revista Weekly Shonen Jump tenemos un vistazo del equipo The Big 3 en la cuarta temporada de Boku no Hero Academia.

Desde que se presentó el primer teaser de la cuarta temporada de Boku no Hero Academia, pues no ha habido mucha información que digamos. Sí, sabemos que el equipo detrás de la música está ya trabajando en My Hero Academia, como se conoce en Occidente a la serie. Una…
